category: Libs
requires: cygwin libccd2
sdesc: "Library for collision detection between convex shapes (licensing & readmes)"
ldesc: "libccd implements variation on Gilbert-Johnson-Keerthi (GJK) algorithm
+ Expand Polytope Algorithm (EPA). It also implements Minkowski Portal
Refinement (MPR, a.k.a. XenoCollide) algorithm as published in Game
Programming Gems 7."
